# .pack-ignore for the KOI Content Extension pack.
#
# Format (INI): one [file:<basename>] section per file, with a comma-separated
# ignore=<validation codes> key. Example:
#
#   [file:playbook-KOI_Ext_-_Alert_Triage.yml]
#   ignore=BA101
#
# No validations are suppressed at present. Add sections here only for findings
# that have been reviewed and deliberately accepted; do not use this file to
# silence BA101 (id != name) or PA128 (missing pack files) — both are fixed in
# the content itself.
